    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Missile Survivor</strong> is a 2D DogFight arcade game, where you can enjoy the thrill of dogfighting in a 2D space. Choose the best aircraft and weapons to survive until the end and become the ace of aerial combat! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Engage in intense battles with numerous enemy planes!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243930/extras/0fde173537c5e62a09171ca71a5cb849.poster.avif?t=1728700080\" width=564 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243930/extras/0fde173537c5e62a09171ca71a5cb849.webm?t=1728700080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243930/extras/0fde173537c5e62a09171ca71a5cb849.mp4?t=1728700080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose your aircraft and upgrade your abilities!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243930/extras/36e6f0b100ed9e20ea6952ecf30f2027.poster.avif?t=1728700080\" width=564 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243930/extras/36e6f0b100ed9e20ea6952ecf30f2027.webm?t=1728700080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243930/extras/36e6f0b100ed9e20ea6952ecf30f2027.mp4?t=1728700080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enemy aces are tougher than you think!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243930/extras/4d80b8b3e374b8ae5f21cfb5f8027af6.poster.avif?t=1728700080\" width=564 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243930/extras/4d80b8b3e374b8ae5f21cfb5f8027af6.webm?t=1728700080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243930/extras/4d80b8b3e374b8ae5f21cfb5f8027af6.mp4?t=1728700080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 types of aircraft</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 types of special weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deploy flares</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect experience to upgrade abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced combat</p></li></ul>",
